data.description: Welcome to this spacious home located in the growing town of Broussard! You are sure to love this open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining! The living area and dining room are sure to shine with all the natural light coming in from the large bay windows! Envision relaxing in the evenings while sitting in front of your brick wood burning fireplace! The kitchen opens to all main areas of the home, has a breakfast bar, and a farmhouse inspired stainless steel sink. Off from the main living areas of the home is a separate sitting area that can be used as a den, playroom, office, exercise area... the possibilities are endless! There is also an upstairs loft area that can be used in multiple ways... you really do have to see all this home has to offer!
